title: Introduction to Python
description: In this blog post, I will be going through the basics of Python.

body.raw:
## Setting up the Python environment

asda asda

## Writing your first line of Python

Now that all of your development environment has been setup, let's begin coding.
Usually, every beginner starts by writing the famous [Hello, World!](https://justbrandonlim.com/blog/hello-world)
program.

Let's try to make Python say "Hello, World!". Write the following line in your code editor.

```python title="Python"
print("Hello, World!")
```
